    dc:description "FIGURES 1–19. Light micrographs of Brachysira heteropolaris Van de Vijver sp. nov. LM images taken from the holotype population (IX-18-A8, Weissflog slide Loch Canmor, Aberdeenshire 2, Scotland, UK). LM views of the population arranged in decreasing length. Scale bar = 10 µm." ;
